question:
Find $\tan G$ in the right triangle shown below.

[asy]

pair H,F,G;

H = (0,0);

G = (15,0);

F = (0,8);

draw(F--G--H--F);

draw(rightanglemark(F,H,G,20));

label("$H$",H,SW);

label("$G$",G,SE);

label("$F$",F,N);

label("$17$",(F+G)/2,NE);

label("$15$",G/2,S);

[/asy]

In right triangle $XYZ$, shown below, what is $\sin{X}$?

[asy]
draw((0,0)--(10,0)--(3.6,4.8)--cycle,black+linewidth(1));
draw(rightanglemark((0,0),(3.6,4.8),(10,0),20),black+linewidth(1));
label("X",(10,0),E);
label("Y",(3.6,4.8),N);
label("Z",(0,0),W);
label("10",(0,0)--(10,0),S);
label("8",(10,0)--(3.6,4.8),NE);
[/asy]

